1. Create Test topic

KafkaHome/bin/kafka-topics.sh --create --zookeeper localhost:2181 --replication-factor 3 --partitions 8 --topic Test-topic

2. Describe of the topic

KafkaHome/bin/kafka-topics.sh --describe --topic Test-topic --zookeeper localhost:2181

3.  List of topics

KafkaHome/bin/kafka-topics.sh --list --zookeeper localhost:2181

4. Check status of syncronization

KafkaHome/bin/zookeeper-shell.sh localhost:2181 ls /brokers/ids

5. publish the topic

KafkaHome/bin/kafka-console-producer.sh --broker-list localhost:9092 --topic Test-topic

6. Consume the topic

KafkaHome/bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic Test-topic --from-beginning --group test-consumer-group

7. Delete Topic 

First we have to stop kafka service on three brokers to run below command
 ps -ef | grep -i kafka 
 kill -9 <kafka pid>

./kafka-topics.sh --zookeeper localhost:2181 --delete --topic Test-topic
KafkaHome/bin/zookeeper-shell.sh localhost:2181 ls /brokers/topics
KafkaHome/bin/zookeeper-shell.sh localhost:2181 deleteall /brokers/topics

8. Create users for ACL auth to kafka topic

KafkaHome/bin/kafka-configs.sh --zookeeper localhost:2181 --alter --add-config 'SCRAM-SHA-256=[password='abc@123']' --entity-type users --entity-name stskafka
KafkaHome/bin/kafka-configs.sh --zookeeper localhost:2181 --alter --add-config 'SCRAM-SHA-256=[password='abc@123']' --entity-type users --entity-name stskafkaz

9. Allow ACL auth to particular topic for publish and cosume in secure way

KafkaHome/bin/kafka-acls.sh --authorizer-properties zookeeper.connect=localhost:2181 --add --allow-principal User:stskafka --operation All --topic Test-topic --cluster

10. Publish topics in secure way 

KafkaHome/bin/kafka-console-producer.sh --broker-list :9093 --topic Test-topic --producer.config KafkaHome/config/dusk.properties
KafkaHome/bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --bootstrap-server localhost:9093 --consumer.config KafkaHome/config/dusk.properties --from-beginning --topic Test-topic
